<HEADLINE>
<P>
LOS ANGELES TEACHERS' STRIKE SETTLEMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Times' coverage of the strike was enriched by Marita Hernandez's articles. 
She helped all of us gain insight into the personal turmoils of the strike by 
interviewing the administration, striking teachers, teachers who crossed the 
picket lines, as well as the students of Le Conte Junior High. Her effort to 
elicit all sides of a difficult issue is to be commended. 
</P>
<P>
ANN BLAU 
</P>
<P>
Hermosa Beach 
</P>
