march as crowd blocks troops headed for Tian An Men Square in Beijing. ; Photo, 
Student displays rifle from window of troop bus that protesters seized in 
Beijing. Thousands swarmed around military vehicles. Associated Press; Map, 
Tian An Men Square, Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
