<HEADLINE>
<P>
JOFFREY CHANGES OPENING DATE OF 'NUTCRACKER' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Joffrey Ballet will open its engagement of the "Nutcracker" at the Orange 
County Performing Arts Center on Dec. 13, one day later than originally 
announced. 
</P>
<P>
Another performance has been added, Dec. 17 at 7:30 p.m., to make up the 
difference. 
</P>
<P>
The opening was postponed because of a change in the Joffrey's touring 
schedule, Center officials said Friday. The complete new schedule of 
performances is as follows: Dec. 13 through 16 at 8 p.m.; Dec. 16 at 2 p.m., 
Dec. 17 at 2 and 7:30 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
Further information is available at (714) 556-2787. 
</P>
